cer, and the video was for someone else=E2=80=99s channel. But once =0Ashe =
went viral she was maximally interested inbecoming part of the fame =0Aecon=
omy. How does one do that=3F How does one parlay one brief funny viral clip=
 =0Ainto a lucrative career=3F There are well-understood approaches. You ca=
n probably =0Aget into reality television, perhaps followed by politics. Yo=
u can get paid to =0Apromote products =E2=80=94 in ads, or on your own soci=
