 sell merch. If you can sing or act, you =0Ause your viral fame as a way in=
to a singing or acting career. It is 2024, so =0AWelch literallyhas a podca=
st =0A<https://open.spotify.com/show/7KCh1Z181LOIh3IP6EbqNR>.=0A=0ABut in 2=
024 there is a much, much, much, much, much better answer. Modern =0Afinanc=
e has created an incredible tool fordirectly monetizing your 15 minutes =0A=
of fame. This tool is the memecoin. A memecoin is a crypto token that is =
