 a day, so you will sell =0Aa lot of them and pocket millions of dollars. A=
nd that=E2=80=99s it, that=E2=80=99s the end. =0AYou don=E2=80=99t have to =
do any other things. You have gone viral and then fully, =0Adirectly moneti=
zed your virality.=0A=0AI should say that, while this is an utterly amazing=
